00:04:19.958 --> 00:04:21.722
I encourage you to pause this video,

00:04:21.722 --> 00:04:24.578
and figure out what are
the x and y-intercepts

00:04:24.578 --> 00:04:27.620
for the graph that
represents the solutions,

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:31.312
all the xy pairs that
satisfy this equation.

00:04:31.312 --> 00:04:33.680
Well the easiest thing to do here,

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:38.680
let's see what the y value is when x = 0

00:04:38.765 --> 00:04:42.201
and what x value is when y = 0.

00:04:42.201 --> 00:04:46.590
When x = 0 this becomes 6y = 30.

00:04:46.590 --> 00:04:48.354
